title: Adding utility by adding $SHOULDERS, $KNEES, and $TOES
body: Holders of HeadDAO tokens that have staked their tokens would be eligible to mint Shoulders, Knees, and Toes - the next collections in our ecosystem.   Each would have their own token ($SHOULDERS, $KNEES, $TOES) and each would provide their own utility within the HeadDAO ecosystem.
author: 0x85D3c6be944F7fF76968C79Fa7CE409F0a3734B6
